73
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:04,639
You confirmed the symptoms of the patient's condition.

74
00:08:04,639 --> 00:08:06,739
Your effort should be acknowledged.

75
00:08:08,958 --> 00:08:12,000
However, you took your own decision and performed pericardiocentesis on the patient.

76
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,393
Why did you do that?

77
00:08:13,393 --> 00:08:15,380
Because of his condition.

78
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:17,680
Have you done such surgery before?

79
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:20,033
I did it during my internship.

80
00:08:20,033 --> 00:08:21,759
Only during your internship?

81
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:23,120
You were lucky this time.

82
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,519
Will you be as lucky next time?

83
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:26,680
Department Chief, it's not that I was lucky.

84
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:31,411
You said you wouldn't wait for my arrival if the situation was critical, am I right?

85
00:08:31,411 --> 00:08:33,000
Let me ask you this then.

86
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:36,600
Do you wish for the situation to be critical or otherwise?

87
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:40,480
Department Chief, I'm not an idealist.

88
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:43,440
I will take corresponding measures according to the situation I face.

89
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,180
That's all.

90
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:51,220
Xu Qin, do you understand what a doctor's benevolence means?

91
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,897
Department Chief!

92
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:02,980
Our team leader was reprimanded by Department Chief Xu again.

93
00:09:04,095 --> 00:09:05,240
That was to be expected.

94
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:07,514
She was reprimanded even though she saved someone.

95
00:09:07,514 --> 00:09:09,679
Don't you think that's unfair?

96
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:11,360
Now that she has offended Department Chief Xu,

97
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:15,320
I'm sure her slot in the research team will be affected.

98
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:17,960
Department Chief Xu didn't like her from the start.

99
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:20,760
She always pulls a long face, unlike Dr. Yang.

100
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:23,159
Dr. Yang cares for her patients. She's friendly too.

101
00:09:23,159 --> 00:09:24,759
There's nothing wrong with that.

102
00:09:24,759 --> 00:09:26,999
It's fine as long as she can save people. 
    

103
00:10:02,669 --> 00:10:05,200
Miao Miao, when will your cousin come back?

104
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:07,199
I think he'll be home soon.

105
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,620
Brother, you're back.

106
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:18,159
Brother, let me introduce them to you.

107
00:10:18,159 --> 00:10:19,559
These are my classmates.

108
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:21,080
This is Yi Yue. This is Ye Zi.

109
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,799
This is Yuan Yuan. This is my cousin.

110
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:24,691
- Hello, Brother. 
 - Hi, Brother.

111
00:10:24,691 --> 00:10:26,292
Hello.

112
00:10:29,719 --> 00:10:31,080
What do you think about my cousin?

113
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,759
I can finally see him in person.

114
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:34,600
He's much hotter in real life.

115
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,769
That's for sure.

116
00:10:36,769 --> 00:10:38,639
By the way, I'll help my cousin to clean the house first.

117
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:40,040
You guys can have a seat inside.

118
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:41,559
Go ahead.

119
00:10:41,559 --> 00:10:44,620
He's so hot.

120
00:10:47,848 --> 00:10:49,320
Where are your parents?

121
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:51,360
They went to the park for a walk.

122
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:53,086
They prepared our meal before they left.

123
00:10:53,086 --> 00:10:55,522
We starved as we waited for you to come back.

124
00:10:55,522 --> 00:10:57,159
Why were you waiting for me?

125
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:59,039
They thought you were hot after looking at your picture.

126
00:10:59,039 --> 00:11:00,979
They wanted to have a meal with you.

127
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:03,663
Zhai Miao, are you out of your mind?

128
00:11:03,663 --> 00:11:05,919
If you have so much free time, you can get yourself a boyfriend.

129
00:11:05,919 --> 00:11:07,840
Do you think I'm a monkey in the zoo?

130
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:10,619
Brother, are you angry?

131
00:11:10,619 --> 00:11:12,300
I just thought that I had a hot older brother.

132
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:14,879
That's why I wanted to show off in front of my classmates.

133
00:11:14,879 --> 00:11:17,780
Don't embarrass me, okay?

134
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:22,039
- Don't do this again. 
 - Okay.

135
00:11:22,039 --> 00:11:23,284
Let's go.

136
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:41,700
Here, have some water.

137
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:43,840
It's so hot out here.

138
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:47,080
Do you think Zhai Miao's plan will work?

139
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:49,320
Why are we doing this too?

140
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:51,879
I don't care if it'll work or not. Let's just give it a try.

141
00:11:51,879 --> 00:11:55,799
Every time I arrange a blind date for him, he says that he's busy with work.

142
00:11:55,799 --> 00:11:58,120
Besides, we're doing this for his sake.

143
00:11:58,120 --> 00:12:00,639
I think arranging the blind date at home is a good idea.

144
00:12:00,639 --> 00:12:02,155
I don't expect much from my future daughter-in-law.

145
00:12:02,155 --> 00:12:06,114
I think anyone is a good match for him as long as she's not related to the Meng family.

146
00:12:06,679 --> 00:12:10,898
God, please be kind to Yan'er this time.

147
00:12:10,898 --> 00:12:14,080
I still remember he came to our house

148
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:16,280
when he was still a child.

149
00:12:17,799 --> 00:12:19,695
 Who's there? It's so late. 

150
00:12:19,695 --> 00:12:21,260
 - So cold. 
 - Coming. 

151
00:12:21,260 --> 00:12:22,782
 You're right. 

152
00:12:23,527 --> 00:12:24,969
 Uncle! 

153
00:12:25,788 --> 00:12:26,840
 What are you doing here? 

154
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:28,320
 Child, why are you wearing so little clothes? 

155
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,679
 Yes. Hurry and come inside. 

156
00:12:29,679 --> 00:12:31,900
 I think Dad is dead. 

157
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,564
 What did you say? 

158
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:40,577
 When I left the house, 

159
00:12:40,577 --> 00:12:43,300
 I saw him lying outside. 

160
00:12:43,300 --> 00:12:45,097
 He was motionless. 

161
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,559
 Uncle, 

162
00:12:47,559 --> 00:12:49,679
 I couldn't move him myself. 

163
00:12:49,679 --> 00:12:53,800
 Can you please help me? 

164
00:12:59,145 --> 00:13:01,039
 It was so cold back then. 

165
00:13:01,039 --> 00:13:02,820
 And he was so young. 

166
00:13:03,399 --> 00:13:07,560
I had no idea how he came to our house on foot.

167
00:13:08,639 --> 00:13:11,879
- His mother... 
 - His mother wasn't a good person.

168
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:13,159
His mother was proud and vain.

169
00:13:13,159 --> 00:13:15,399
She could even abandon her own son.

170
00:13:15,399 --> 00:13:18,279
Don't bring her up in front of me again.

171
00:13:18,279 --> 00:13:20,780
I'm just scared.

172
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,519
Yan'er is honest and single-minded.

173
00:13:23,519 --> 00:13:25,540
He's just like his father.

174
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,979
Don't tell me he'll get a partner like his father...

175
00:13:27,979 --> 00:13:31,159
Knock on wood. What are you saying?

176
00:13:32,609 --> 00:13:33,799
Don't spout nonsense.

177
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:37,316
She went overseas, right? Why did she come back?

178
00:13:37,316 --> 00:13:40,720
I mean, it's okay for her to come back. But why did she come to our house?

179
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,399
What exactly is she up to?

180
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:43,800
I don't care what she's up to.

181
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:47,141
This time, I won't let Yan'er get hurt again.

182
00:13:51,159 --> 00:13:53,600
It's so hot here. Why didn't you bring an umbrella with you?

183
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,639
It's too hot.

184
00:13:54,639 --> 00:13:56,360
We can get some calcium from the sun.

185
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:59,559
You usually don't like being under the sunlight. Get some sun and calcium while we're here.

186
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:02,241
- You got osteoporosis, right? 
 -  You got osteoporosis.

187
00:14:02,241 --> 00:14:03,427
It's good to get some sunlight once in a while.

188
00:14:03,427 --> 00:14:05,424
Fine, I'll do it myself.

189
00:14:08,767 --> 00:14:12,251
Miao Miao, your mother is a great cook.

190
00:14:12,251 --> 00:14:15,460
- Yeah, right? 
 - Especially the shrimp. They taste heavenly.

191
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:18,138
You guys can have more if you like them. Don't be courteous.

192
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,279
Ye Zi, eat up.

193
00:14:23,279 --> 00:14:24,831
Don't just have that.

194
00:14:24,831 --> 00:14:26,519
Here, try this.

195
00:14:26,519 --> 00:14:28,005
Thank you.

196
00:14:49,039 --> 00:14:52,079
Brother, Miao Miao said that you were a firefighter.

197
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:55,144
Is your work dangerous?

198
00:14:55,144 --> 00:14:56,399
It's okay.

199
00:14:56,399 --> 00:14:57,759
Fires don't occur frequently.

200
00:14:57,759 --> 00:14:59,159
We often deal with daily rescue missions.

201
00:14:59,159 --> 00:15:01,740
However, it's dangerous when the situations are dangerous.

202
00:15:03,437 --> 00:15:07,159
If so, Brother, why haven't you got yourself a girlfriend yet?

203
00:15:09,407 --> 00:15:12,143
For no reason. I had my hands tied at work.

204
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:14,347
Why are you asking so many questions?

205
00:15:14,347 --> 00:15:16,120
Is this a census survey?

206
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:18,020
That's not it.

207
00:15:28,795 --> 00:15:31,279
You guys can go ahead. I have something else to attend to.

208
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:45,200
Don't tell me your cousin was upset with us?

209
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:47,059
No way.

210
00:15:47,059 --> 00:15:50,799
Miao Miao, your cousin was checking Ye Zi out.

211
00:15:50,799 --> 00:15:54,100
Yeah, right? You saw that, too?

212
00:15:54,100 --> 00:15:56,679
If so, I'll head upstairs and inquire about it.

213
00:15:56,679 --> 00:15:58,303
Hurry up then.

214
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:10,570
Brother, what are you looking for?

215
00:16:10,570 --> 00:16:12,360
My lighter. Have you seen it?

216
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,759
Your lighter?

217
00:16:13,759 --> 00:16:15,639
It's not like it's a rare item.

218
00:16:15,639 --> 00:16:17,679
Just buy another one if you lose it.

219
00:16:19,012 --> 00:16:19,919
Brother.

220
00:16:19,919 --> 00:16:22,849
Brother, I have something to ask you. Come.

221
00:16:22,849 --> 00:16:24,840
What do you think about Ye Zi?

222
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:26,200
Which one is Ye Zi?

223
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:29,680
It's the girl who spoke the least and looked like Xu Qin.

224
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:32,600
Who said she looked like her?

225
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:34,159
Brother, listen to me.

226
00:16:34,159 --> 00:16:35,519
She's my best buddy.

227
00:16:35,519 --> 00:16:38,491
From my buddy to my sister-in-law. Isn't that great?

228
00:16:43,919 --> 00:16:45,559
You're itching for a beating, huh?

229
00:16:45,559 --> 00:16:47,180
Brother, I'm being serious here.

230
00:16:47,180 --> 00:16:49,419
You should consider it.

231
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:54,200
Brother, you should consider it.

232
00:16:54,200 --> 00:16:56,719
I know my fault now.

233
00:16:59,286 --> 00:17:01,000
I'm serious. You should consider it.

234
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,461
Get out!

235
00:17:09,062 --> 00:17:10,796
   

236
00:17:14,559 --> 00:17:16,119
Hello, Xiao Yi Xiao?

237
00:17:16,119 --> 00:17:17,409
Hello?

238
00:17:17,409 --> 00:17:18,638
I made the inquiry for you.

239
00:17:18,638 --> 00:17:20,350
Did you find him?

240
00:17:20,350 --> 00:17:23,143
Song something is on leave today.

241
00:17:23,143 --> 00:17:25,440
Why are you inquiring about him?

242
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:26,960
Don't ask.

243
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:30,160
Your mother and brother would skin me alive if they found out, you know?

244
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:31,800
I'll buy you a meal next time.

245
00:17:31,800 --> 00:17:34,381
Yeah, and you never do.

246
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:39,012
Hello?

247
00:17:54,519 --> 00:17:56,279
Song Yan.

248
00:18:00,279 --> 00:18:01,982
Are you passing by again?

249
00:18:03,279 --> 00:18:05,319
I wasn't passing by.

250
00:18:05,319 --> 00:18:07,211
I came here on purpose.

251
00:18:07,839 --> 00:18:09,471
Do you need anything?

252
00:18:11,519 --> 00:18:13,299
I'm here to return your uniform.

253
00:18:16,362 --> 00:18:18,160
You saved me last time.

254
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:20,139
I'm here to thank you.

255
00:18:24,279 --> 00:18:26,419
You came all the way here just to tell me that?

256
00:18:30,042 --> 00:18:32,112
I'm here to thank you.

257
00:18:32,112 --> 00:18:34,920
Fine. How do you plan to thank me?

258
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:38,320
How do you want me to thank you?

259
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:45,440
What if I want you to marry me?

260
00:19:03,732 --> 00:19:07,801
If I told all the people I rescued to marry me, I should be dead by then.

261
00:19:07,801 --> 00:19:09,781
It will never be your turn.

262
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:12,652
Xu Qin,

263
00:19:12,652 --> 00:19:14,599
where did you get the confidence

264
00:19:14,599 --> 00:19:19,000
